  "2371240": {
    "name": "DOLOS: Your Best Future",
    "steam_appid": 2371240,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In this narrative management game, you will have to decide about the future of everyone according to the anticipations of an AI. Help create the efficient society of tomorrow or preserve the dreams and hopes of everybody. Your choices will affect the future of Gauetia.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/93ff197c4d6cd5895910d617c5cde4c6.poster.avif?t=1767831832\" width=620 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/93ff197c4d6cd5895910d617c5cde4c6.webm?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/93ff197c4d6cd5895910d617c5cde4c6.mp4?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/4109b44ad93df0a5bc5cf486ceaad552.poster.avif?t=1767831832\" width=1170 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/4109b44ad93df0a5bc5cf486ceaad552.webm?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/4109b44ad93df0a5bc5cf486ceaad552.mp4?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After an unprecedented economic crisis and to deal with mass unemployment, the government of Gauetia appoints a young company, <i>DOLOS Incorporated</i>, to create a program capable of coordinating job and training seekers (students, unemployed) with the labour market in order to build a perfectly efficient society. <br><br><strong>Capable of predicting the potential of each individual through large-scale data collection</strong>, DOLOS will become<strong> a central AI in the government's economic and social policy</strong>, but not without causing some damage...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Theophile Agnos, an operator performing all kinds of micro-tasks on a daily basis. Although the tasks on the DOLOS app are underpaid, they have the advantage of being a video game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/997cc199c50b2fe93908405b180e07d4.poster.avif?t=1767831832\" width=1170 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/997cc199c50b2fe93908405b180e07d4.webm?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/997cc199c50b2fe93908405b180e07d4.mp4?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Working on DOLOS is <strong>playing a management game and a card game, so that a group of applicants have a place for life</strong> in the perfectly efficient society dreamed up by DOLOS. <br><br>In the first game, <strong>select the best applicants</strong> applying for training. <strong>Add new data</strong> about them to the system. <strong>The more positive data you can identify</strong>, the more applicants you will be able to select!  <br><br>In the second game, <strong>your time is running out!</strong> <strong>Draw your applicant-cards</strong> and place them in training courses, preferably those recommended by DOLOS! The more you follow DOLOS' recommendations, the more bonus time you will earn, the more cards you will draw, and <strong>the longer your turn will last</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/a0659a85f84ee4a5cddad7b4d4175e75.poster.avif?t=1767831832\" width=1170 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/a0659a85f84ee4a5cddad7b4d4175e75.webm?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/a0659a85f84ee4a5cddad7b4d4175e75.mp4?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/cb2871df0fbbc1411352e6c0366d2fa7.poster.avif?t=1767831832\" width=1170 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/cb2871df0fbbc1411352e6c0366d2fa7.webm?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/cb2871df0fbbc1411352e6c0366d2fa7.mp4?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Talk to your performance coach OJO,</strong> optimize your productivity, <strong>earn even more EXP</strong>.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete progressive challenges, climb the operator hierarchy and earn unique perks! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Will you become the best operator at DOLOS Incorporated?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/7522860a4dc74e3affa486e19638b7b9.poster.avif?t=1767831832\" width=1170 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/7522860a4dc74e3affa486e19638b7b9.webm?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/7522860a4dc74e3affa486e19638b7b9.mp4?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Talk your colleague Marie, </strong>together<strong> investigate the hidden aspects </strong>of the software.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover the stories</strong> of applicants condemned by DOLOS, <strong>bypass DOLOS' rules </strong>to help those applicants slip through the cracks. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>But don't get fired! If you run out of EXP, you're out!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/7eb0d8426beea669b9ecb31e4dbcc907.poster.avif?t=1767831832\" width=1170 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/7eb0d8426beea669b9ecb31e4dbcc907.webm?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/7eb0d8426beea669b9ecb31e4dbcc907.mp4?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contribute to the creation of <strong>a perfectly efficient society</strong>...or fight against the system<strong> to respect everyone's aspirations and freedom</strong>. Confront the destinies of the applicants, ask yourself what is the fairest for each one of them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/eb71a9bd24c723893fcbdfb72d5d3ab2.poster.avif?t=1767831832\" width=1170 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/eb71a9bd24c723893fcbdfb72d5d3ab2.webm?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371240/extras/eb71a9bd24c723893fcbdfb72d5d3ab2.mp4?t=1767831832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Observe the consequences of your choices <strong>as the years go by</strong>.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Re-discover applicants from past years and <strong>see what they become</strong>.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Keep abreast of current events in Gauetia</strong>, seek out new information that can open up new narrative path, and learn more about the characters behind DOLOS.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Develop</strong> (or not) <strong>the relationship with your interlocutors</strong> to find out more about their role in <strong>this gripping story with many twists and variations</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>All your choices - and those of the other operators - will determine Gauetia's future!</i></p>",
